{"tid":799716,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"關東關西煮肉文化的差異 牛鍋 vs 壽喜燒","createTime":"2018-08-30T09:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T09:55:37.000Z","uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ecfb2b535cdd127c72093cbffb1d35e882a85ef","tid":799716,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"在明治時期，坊間傳言：日本人之所以矮小，在身高、體格上都不如外國人，歸根究柢因為日本人自古以來沒有吃肉的習慣。基於這個論調，當時著名的思想家福澤諭吉鼓吹吃肉，並聳人耳聽地說，不吃肉就體力虛弱，體力虛弱就有亡國的危機。<br />\n<br />\n在明治五年（1872年）一月二十四日，明治天皇下令試吃牛肉，並讓報紙大肆報道天皇吃牛肉的消息，希望做到率先垂範。如是者，民眾一窩蜂地開始吃牛；而被開放為通商口岸的大城市，像橫濱、江戶（東京的舊稱）也陸陸續續出現牛肉火鍋店。這種牛肉鍋是在平底鍋裏放入大葱、豆腐、蒟蒻絲和用醬油、砂糖所調的醬汁，把牛肉灼煮。如此說來，不是很像&rdquo;sukiyaki&rdquo;「壽喜燒」（又稱為鋤燒）嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wwuFLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wwuFLM&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=f94c106d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2wwuFLM</a>"},{"pid":"a085f0d3e1903b5412be62d8c07fc9c5973fad67","tid":799716,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"肥牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9965ea3bbcbcdbab49c8c72f23ad934944eacdb","tid":799716,"uid":150421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"關關東關西文化差異咩事"},{"pid":"2f3628f6558cca80351d00ed99443db960a3929b","tid":799716,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:55:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/http://bit.ly/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fhtt